Properties
Title
public string Title { get; set }

The title of the menu entry, or null if none.  This can only be null if the entry is not expected to be displayed, such as a container that will be collapsed.

Parent
public Base.Container Parent { get; set }

The parent of this entry, or null if none.

ExtraData
public object ExtraData { get; set }

A object reference that can be used to attach arbitrary data to an individual entry.  This can be used to aid code that converts the menu to an output format.
